name: VSMod
description: A moderation and utility cog for managing warnings, bans, mutes, banned words, invite link blocking and other features like suggestions.
end_user_data_statement: data such as UIDs of server members and Moderators along with GuildID and RoleID may be stored by the cog for keeping track of user warnings, mutes, bans, and offenses
install_msg: Thank you for installing VSMod, to get a list of commands use [p]help VSMod
author: Amateur-God
